data.description: This property checks all of the boxes on almost any buyers list: cul-de-sac, private back yard with large deck and patio, granite countertops with an island in the kitchen, gas stove, good size primary bedroom with two walk in closets, plus a soaking tub, tiled shower, and two sinks in both the primary bathroom and hall bathroom!  The downstairs heat pump is only 4 years old, and the upstairs heat pump was replaced two years ago.  The attached two car garage is oversized for extra storage, plus there is a storage shed.  Don’t wait, call today for your private showing!
